description: Deletes all resources and information related to a fleet and shuts down any currently running fleet instances, including those in remote locations. To delete a fleet, specify the fleet ID to be terminated. During the deletion process, the fleet status is changed to DELETING. When completed, the status switches to TERMINATED and the fleet event FLEET_DELETED is emitted. Setting up Amazon GameLift Fleets.

parameters.name: FleetId
parameters.description: A unique identifier for the fleet to be deleted. You can use either the fleet ID or ARN value.
